        "content": "## AI Ops Approval Workflow\\n\\n1. POST to `/webhook/ai-ops-request` with `X-Webhook-Secret`.\\n2. n8n calls the FastAPI backend using `AI_OPS_API_BASE_URL` and `AI_OPS_API_KEY`.\\n3. Backend classifies the request with mock or OpenAI LLM mode.\\n4. If `requires_human_review` is true, POST to `/webhook/ai-ops-decision` with the secret and decision payload.\\n\\nNo credentials are stored in this workflow export.",
